# This is a simple telegram bot.

You can call @haoxiangpeng_bot to add it to your group or chat with him


Some avaliable command:
    '/study <seconds>'  to study
    '/echo <message>' to echo message
    '/worst' to list worst language
    '/best' to show the best language ever
    '/chat <message>' to chat with bot freely
    '/retrive' retrive message in the data base
    '/AC <number1>C<number2>'Calculate Permutations and Combinations
    '/start' Say hi

Attention:
    1. I will record all your conversations for anonymous use.
    
    2. You should genernate a 'key.txt' in your work folder,where
       the first line should be telegram bot key
       the second line should be turing bot key

